+.TH tlslookup 1
+.SH NAME
+.B tlslookup - resolve the internet address with DNS queries over HTTPS/TLS
+.SH SYNOPSIS
+.B tlslookup <host>
+.SH DESCRIPTION
+Similar to nslookup(1), tlslookup is a program to query internet
+domain name servers. Tlslookup resolves the internet address of <host>
+with DNS queries over HTTPS/TLS by talking to the nss-tlsd(8) daemon.
